// [vNEXT] Unified icon resolution across both families. Precedence:
//   1. Active theme's override for this key (stroke path string, OR a
//      { fill: 'aeKey' } tag routing to the AEFillIcons family)
//   2. CyberIcons[icon]   -> stroke family (24x24, unthemed default)
//   3. AEFillIcons[icon]  -> fill family (512x512) — a same-named fallback,
//      so adding an AEFillIcons entry with an icon's existing name upgrades
//      it everywhere (any getCyberIconHTML/createCyberIcon/$.svg call site)
//      without touching AE_THEME_ICONS or the call site at all.
//   4. not found -> { kind: null }
// _aeIconExists() is the gate other code should use instead of checking
